These are Puzzles for 4x7 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 4x7-Level-1-1::.
The people have 7 different jobs:  firefighter, designer, scientist, writer, analyst, pilot, fisherman
The people have 7 different hobbies: hiking, video-games, reading, drawing, sudoku, magic-tricks, woodworking
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: scientistsy, family, adventure, spy, epic, scientific, documentary
House: modern, farmhouse, tower, victorian, townhouse, futuristic, cape-cod
 1. the firefighter is on the left of the fisherman##1
 2. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the right of the person watching scientistsy movies##1
 3. the modern house is the person watching epic movies##1
 4. the person watching epic movies is on the right of the person watching family movies##1
 5. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the far left##1
 6. the tower house is on the right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
 7. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the right of the writer##1
 8. the farmhouse house is on the right of the townhouse house##1
 9. the person who's hobby is reading is on the far right##1
10. the person who's hobby is reading is on the right of the townhouse house##1
11. the pilot is in the middle##1
12. the scientist is on the far left##1
13. the person who's hobby is sudoku is in the middle##1
14. the person watching scientific movies is on the left of the person watching adventure movies##1
15. the cape-cod house is on the left of the firefighter##1
16. the person watching epic movies is on the left of the person watching scientific movies##1
17. the futuristic house is on the right of the cape-cod house##1
18. the person who's hobby is reading is on the right of the person watching spy movies##1
19. the tower house is in the middle##1
20. the person watching spy movies is on the left of the designer##1
21. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the right of the writer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |   3    |     4      |    5     |     6      |       7       |
| Job      | scientist    | firefighter     | fisherman  | pilot   | writer | analyst      | designer          |
| Hobby   | woodworking    | drawing   | magic-tricks  | sudoku       | hiking  | video-games      | reading     |
| Movie-Genre         | scientistsy | family | epic | scientific | adventure   | spy     | documentary |
| House     | cape-cod      | futuristic   | modern   | tower  | victorian  | townhouse | farmhouse       |

