7 different games are played: canasta, scrabble, bridge, poker, backgammon, go, whist
The people have 7 different hobbies: skydiving, magic-tricks, singing, filmmaking, hiking, baking, video-games
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: folk, ambient, blues, gospel, classical, hip-hop, indie
 1. the person playing bridge is on the right of the person playing scrabble##1
 2. the fan of blues is on the right of the owner of the cat##1
 3. the person playing go is the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
 4. the person who's hobby is baking is on the far left##1
 5. the owner of the cat is on the right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
 6. the person playing poker is on the far left##1
 7. the person who's hobby is singing is on the right of the fan of blues##1
 8. the person playing backgammon is the owner of the mouse##1
 9. the fan of ambient is the owner of the guinea-pig##1
10. the person who's hobby is hiking is in the middle##1
11. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the right of the fan of hip-hop##1
12. the person who's hobby is baking is the fan of gospel##1
13. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the left of the person who's hobby is singing##1
14. the fan of folk is on the right of the person playing backgammon##1
15. the owner of the chinchilla is on the right of the owner of the bird##1
16. the person who's hobby is baking is the fan of gospel##1
17. the person playing go is on the right of the owner of the hamster##1
18. the person who's hobby is singing is on the left of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
19. the fan of classical is the person playing bridge##1
20. the person playing canasta is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |     3     |     4      |      5       |       6       |     7      |
| Pet           | rabbit | hamster    | guinea-pig     | cat    | mouse   | bird | chinchilla   |
